Package UI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddAppointment
    Creates the frame to add a new appointment.
    AddPatient
    Creates the frame to add a new patient.
    AppointmentForm
    Creates the frame with all the data for a specific appointment.
    Appointments
    Creates the JPanel that we will attach to the Home with information about appointments (A table and a couple of buttons).
    HomePage
    Implements the main JFrame to which the three UIs are added.
    ImportExport
    The third JPanel is used to attach a couple of buttons to the main frame.
    LoginPage
    The first frame that allows to login in the app.
    MorePhotos
    To access three more photos.
    PatientForm
    Creates the frame to see all the data for a specific Patient.
    Patients
    Has the elements needed to fill the central and lower part of the HomePage regarding patients.
    SearchAppointment
    Creates the form to find selected appointments.
    SearchPatient
    Creates the frame to find selected patients.
